            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3ERestoration%20is%20such%20a%20biblical%20idea.%20The%20Bible%20is%20full%20of%20stories%20of%20broken%20lives%2C%20wrecked%20dreams%2C%20and%20dashed%20hopes.%20But%20in%20these%20stories%2C%20the%20power%20of%20faith%20brings%20such%20a%20dramatic%20turnaround%20in%20each%20situation%20that%20the%20people%20involved%20cannot%20contain%20their%20emotions.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThere%20may%20have%20been%20a%20situation%20you%20practically%20gave%20up%20on%2C%20but%20then%20God%20reversed%20it%20miraculously.%20Perhaps%20Psalm%20126%3A2%20describes%20how%20you%20and%20your%20loved%20ones%20felt%20as%20you%20laughed%20and%20joyfully%20sang%20aloud%20of%20the%20Lord's%20deliverance.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EHosea%206%3A2%20(NIV)%20describes%20a%20scene%20of%20two%20days%20of%20death%20and%20a%20third%20day%20of%20resurrection%3A%20%22After%20two%20days%20he%20will%20revive%20us%3B%20on%20the%20third%20day%20he%20will%20restore%20us%2C%20that%20we%20may%20live%20in%20his%20presence.%22%20%20This%20is%20a%20direct%20prophecy%20of%20Jesus'%20resurrection%20on%20the%20third%20day.%20His%20disciples%20had%20lost%20all%20hope%2C%20when%20suddenly%20He%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20grave!%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMaybe%20today%20your%20hopes%20are%20lying%20dead%20inside%20the%20grave%20with%20Satan's%20guards%20at%20the%20door.%20Take%20courage-the%20third%20day%20is%20coming!%20%22Restore%20our%20fortunes%2C%20Lord%2C%20as%20streams%20renew%20the%20desert.%20Those%20who%20plant%20in%20tears%20will%20harvest%20with%20shouts%20of%20joy.%20They%20weep%20as%20they%20go%20to%20plant%20their%20seed%2C%20but%20they%20sing%20as%20they%20return%20with%20the%20harvest%22%20(Psalm%20126%3A4-6).%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
