            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EHosea%206%3A1-9%3A17%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22hose_6_1%22%20bk%3D%22hose%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EHosea%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EA%20Call%20to%20Repentance%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BCome%2C%20let%20us%20return%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EHe%20has%20torn%20us%20to%20pieces%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Enow%20he%20will%20heal%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EHe%20has%20injured%20us%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Enow%20he%20will%20bandage%20our%20wounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22hose_6_2%22%20bk%3D%22hose%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20just%20a%20short%20time%20he%20will%20restore%20us%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eso%20that%20we%20may%20live%20in%20his%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22hose_6_3%22%20bk%3D%22hose%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EOh%2C%20that%20we%20might%20know%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3ELet%20us%20press%20on%20to%20know%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EHe%20will%20respond%20to%20us%20as%20surely%20as%20the%20arrival%20of%20dawn%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eor%20the%20coming%20of%20rains%20in%20early%20spring.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22hose_6_4%22%20bk%3D%22hose%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BO%26%23xA0%3BIsrael%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E6%3A4%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EEphraim%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20referring%20to%20the%20northern%20kingdom%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20Judah%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewhat%20should%20I%20do%20with%20you%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20asks%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BFor%20your%20love%20vanishes%20like%20the%20morning%20mist%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20disappears%20like%20dew%20in%20the%20sunlight.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22hose_6_5%22%20bk%3D%22hose%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20sent%20my%20prophets%20to%20cut%20you%20to%20pieces%26%23x2014%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eto%20slaughter%20you%20with%20my%20words%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewith%20judgments%20as%20inescapable%20as%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22hose_6_6%22%20bk%3D%22hose%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20want%20you%20to%20show%20love%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E6%3A6a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Greek%20version%20translates%20this%20Hebrew%20term%20as%20%3Cem%3Eto%20show%20mercy.%3C%2Fem%3E%20Compare%20Matt%209%3A13%3B%2012%3A7.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Enot%20offer%20sacrifices.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EI%20want%20you%20to%20know%20me%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E6%3A6b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20H